server.port=8022

#=================== database config ===================#
database.use_utc_timezore=true
database.enable=false
database.mybatis.enable=true
database.embedded=false
database.url=jdbc:mysql://mysql:3306/dcell_node_service?useUnicode=true&characterEncoding=UTF-8&allowMultiQueries=true&zeroDateTimeBehavior=convertToNull&connectTimeout=5000&socketTimeout=30000
database.username=root
database.password=baidu@2021$

##=================== MQTT config ===================#
mqtt.url=ssl://baetyl-broker.baetyl-edge-system:50010
mqtt.clientId=dcell-node-service
mqtt.automaticReconnect=false
mqtt.cleanSession=true
mqtt.userName=dcell-node-service
mqtt.password=test
mqtt.keepAliveInterval=60
mqtt.qos=1
mqtt.reconnect.baseInterval=1
mqtt.reconnect.maxInterval=1200
mqtt.baetyl.topic=$baetyl/node/props
mqtt.ca.pem=/var/lib/baetyl/system/certs/ca.pem
mqtt.cert.pem=/var/lib/baetyl/system/certs/crt.pem
mqtt.key.pem=/var/lib/baetyl/system/certs/key.pem
mqtt.event.publish=false
mqtt.event.topic=dcell-node-service

##=================== Minio config ===================#
store.on=false
store.endpoint=http://180.76.243.153:9000
store.ak=akakakak
store.sk=sksksksk
store.bucket=dcell-node-service

##=================== file config ===================#
spring.http.multipart.maxFileSize=1024MB
spring.http.multipart.maxRequestSize=1024MB

#=================== logging config ===================#
logging.has_console_appender=false
logging.has_web_debug_appender=false
logging.info_log_file_path=${log.dir}/${service.name}/info/info.log
logging.error_log_file_path=${log.dir}/${service.name}/error/error.log
logging.warn_log_file_path=${log.dir}/${service.name}/warn/warn.log
logging.debug_log_file_path=${log.dir}/${service.name}/debug/debug.log
logging.access_log_file_path=${log.dir}/${service.name}/access/access.log
logging.access_debug_log_file_path=${log.dir}/${service.name}/access_debug/access_debug.log
logging.info_log_max_history_in_hours=168
logging.error_log_max_history_in_days=7
logging.warn_log_max_history_in_days=7
logging.debug_log_max_history_in_days=2
logging.access_log_max_history_in_hours=168
logging.access_debug_log_max_history_in_days=2
